----- Huang Yangzhi

AdminLTE Backend Management System
A powerful backend management system offering multiple interface options and theme customization, suitable for enterprise-level application development and deployment.

✨ Project Features
📝 Supports multiple themes and interface styles
🎨 Responsive design, compatible with various devices
🔧 Highly customizable layouts and components
💾 Server-side data storage with support for multiple databases
🔒 Robust user permission management

------ Huang Yangzhi

------ Huang Jiejing
Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/2217481412huang/j.git
cd j

Install Dependencies

python -m venv myenv
# Activate virtual environment
myenv\Scripts\activate

Launch the Application
python manage.py runserver

The application will be available at:
http://127.0.0.1:8001/

------ Huang Jiejing

------ Huang Zhaomin
Project Structure

SimpleTodo/  
├── public/               # Static assets (contains frontend build files)  
│   └── index.html        # Frontend application entry point  
├── src/                  # Vue.js frontend application  
│   ├── components/       # Vue components  
│   │   └── TodoItem.vue  # Single todo item component  
│   ├── App.vue           # Main interface  
│   ├── main.js           # Application entry point  
│   └── assets/           # Static assets (CSS, images, etc.)  
│       └── styles.css    # Global styles  
├── backend/              # Django backend application  
│   ├── baseapp/          # Django project directory  
│   │   ├── __init__.py  
│   │   ├── settings.py   # Configuration  
│   │   ├── urls.py       # URL routing  
│   │   ├── wsgi.py  
│   │   └── asgi.py  
│   ├── DjangoExtensions/ # Django extension apps (if needed)  
│   │   ├── __init__.py  
│   │   ├── settings.py   # Configuration  
│   │   ├── urls.py       # URL routing  
│   │   ├── wsgi.py  
│   │   └── asgi.py  
│   ├── ExtendUserModel/  # Extended user model app  
│   │   ├── __init__.py  
│   │   ├── models.py     # Database models  
│   │   ├── views.py      # View functions  
│   │   └── urls.py       # URL routing  
│   ├── db.sqlite3        # Database file  
│   ├── manage.py         # Django management script  
│   └── README.md         # Backend documentation  
├── package.json          # Frontend dependencies  
├── README.md             # Project documentation  
└── venv/                 # Virtual environment  
    ├── Lib  
    ├── bin  
    ├── include  
    └── lib  
------ Huang Zhaomin

------ Liang Huafeng, Yu Yongjun

Key Features and Screenshots
Sidebar Navigation:

Multiple sidebar style options: Mini, XS, Flat, Legacy, Compact, Child Indent

Configurable submenu behavior (hide on collapse)

Toggle hover/focus auto-expand functionality

Layout Options:

Fixed page layout toggle

Text Size Customization:

Adjustable text sizes for: Body, Navbar, Brand, Sidebar Navigation, Footer

Navbar Variants:

Color variants: White, Accent, Dark Sidebar, Light Sidebar

Brand Logo Variants:

Customizable logo color schemes

Copyright Information:

Footer displays copyright: "Developed by AdminLTE.io © 2014-2021"

User Profile:

Top-right displays user information (avatar, username, etc.)

Responsive Design:

Adapts to various screen sizes and devices

Theme Customization:

Multiple theme and color scheme options

Multi-language Support:

Built-in internationalization capabilities

Security Features:

User authentication and permission management

Extensibility:

Modular architecture for easy feature expansion

Project Screenshot:
System Interface
Image shows the admin dashboard interface of the management system.

Additional runtime screenshots available in the /images directory

